name: DeFi Kingdoms Guild
description:
We are crowdfunding a Guild that will deploy it's treasury into the Crystalvale expansion of DFK. 

The goal is to raise a pool of capital to enter the ecosystem and create the most rewards for Guild members. We will play the game as a collective using snapshot proposals to vote on strategy, and then airdrop all rewards back to Guild members. 

Participation in the Guild will earn players boosted rewards. This allows small players to earn extra rewards by participating. 

Everything from questing to treasury management are on the table to be voted on!
 

After 1 year players will be able to redeem their tokens for a proportional claim of the remaining treasury. 

Founder doxxed on Gitbook
